data.description: Welcome to this charming colonial nestled at 11 Bills Lane, Milton NY! This spacious 3-bed, 3-bath home spans 2567 sq ft across 1.5 acres on a private cul de sac, offering tranquility and stunning views of the Hudson Valley from its front and back decks. The fenced-in yard provides both security and privacy, ideal for families or pets. Enjoy the warmth of a gas fireplace, the convenience of a 2-car garage, and the allure of an acclaimed school district in this highly coveted area. This is more than a home; it's a haven where comfort meets elegance and breathtaking vistas greet you at every turn!
